---
import Container from "../components/shared/Container.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "2024.12.21"
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <Container>
    <div class="py-20">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">Last Updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
        
        <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">Welcome to ClipTrack, the clipboard management assistant plugin! We highly value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">ClipTrack is a browser extension designed to provide efficient clipboard management. We only collect the minimum amount of information necessary to provide this functionality. All data is stored locally in your browser and is not uploaded to any server. Specifically, we collect:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Clipboard Content:</strong> To provide clipboard management functionality, we need to access and store the content you copy to the clipboard. This content is stored locally in your browser and is not uploaded to our servers.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Usage Data:</strong> To improve our products and services, we may collect anonymous usage data, such as the frequency of your use of the plugin and the features you use. This data does not contain any personally identifiable information and is not uploaded to our servers.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">The information we collect is used for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Providing and Improving Plugin Functionality:</strong> We use your clipboard content to provide the core functionality of the plugin and use anonymous usage data to improve our products and services.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Personalizing Your Experience:</strong> We may use your usage data to provide a more personalized experience.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">4. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We take the following measures to protect your information security:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Local Storage:</strong> Your clipboard content and usage data are stored locally in your browser and are not uploaded to any server.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Data Encryption:</strong> We use encryption technologies to protect your information during transmission and storage.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Access Control:</strong> We restrict access to your information to only those who need to process it.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">5. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">You have the right to access, correct, and delete the information we collect. You can exercise your rights as follows:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Access and Correction:</strong> You can access and correct the clipboard content stored in your local browser at any time.</li>
              <li><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Deletion:</strong> You can delete the clipboard content stored in your local browser at any time, as well as clear the plugin's cache data. Uninstalling the plugin or clearing browser data will also automatically delete all related information.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">6. Changes to the Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p class="mb-4">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make significant changes, we will notify you through appropriate means, such as displaying a notice in the plugin or sending an email.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100">7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us through the following methods:</p>
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg">
              <p class="mb-2"><strong class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:1943875844@qq.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">1943875844@qq.com</a></p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>